---
title: Honey-Soy Pumpkin & Garlic Rice with Greens & Japanese Mayo
description: If you're a long time lover of the honey and soy combo, wait till you try it on roasted pumpkin! Sounds unusual, we know,
but teamed with aromatic ginger veggies and a delectable Japanese mayo, you're in for a real treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-soy-pumpkin-garlic-rice-bowl-69b9673f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/honey-soy-pumpkin-garlic-rice-610b77171d372405c13f635c-bbc0a74f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/honey-soy-pumpkin-and-garlic-rice-610b77171d372405c13f635c
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Asian
nutrition:
  fat: 30.4 g
